<nowiki>ShoesOff</nowiki> is an IRC bouncer written in EmacsLisp, by NicFerrier

An *IRC bouncer* is like a proxy for IRC. It's used to maintain a permanent connection to IRC while you are temporarily offline.

<nowiki>ShoesOff</nowiki> is written with [[rcirc]] but it works with any IRC clients connecting to it.

== Links ==
* [[https://github.com/nicferrier/shoes-off Github Repository]]
* InternetRelayChat

